Name: defaclrole
Description: The OID of the role associated with this entry

Name: defaclnamespace
Description: The OID of the namespace associated with this entry, or 0 if none

Name: defaclobjtype
Description: Type of object this entry is for: r = relation (table, view), S = sequence, f = function, T = type, n = schema

Name: defaclacl
Description: Access privileges that this type of object should have on creation
